From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: S A Muqthyar Ahmed <syed.abdul.muqthyar.ahmed@intel.com>
Date: Mon, 2 Mar 2026 12:36:35 +0530
Subject: drivers/gpu/nvlp: Drop force_probe requirement

Remove the force_probe requirement to enable the platform
-support by default for Xe KMD Backport Kernel.

Signed-off-by: S A Muqthyar Ahmed <syed.abdul.muqthyar.ahmed@intel.com>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_pci.c | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_pci.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_pci.c
index bd5356c62..c0c371e58 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_pci.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/xe/xe_pci.c
@@ -457,7 +457,6 @@ static const struct xe_device_desc nvlp_desc = {
 	.has_page_reclaim_hw_assist = true,
 	.has_pre_prod_wa = true,
 	.max_gt_per_tile = 2,
-	.require_force_probe = true,
 	.va_bits = 48,
 	.vm_max_level = 4,
 };
